sections.heading: Code; general and special provisions
sections.text: In the construction of this code each general provision shall be controlled by a special provision on the same subject, if there is a conflict.SourceG.S.1873, c. 58, § 250, p. 782;R.S.1913, § 8905;C.S.1922, § 9926;C.S.1929, § 29-105;R.S.1943, § 29-105.Annotations
